item.description:
@Tatemo wrote:

Look if you think you can fit a HD models to a 317 char perfectly you go ahead and do it i did it the best i could if you think you can do better do it i think it looks fine myself and its the best anyone has done AND released. Yes i know SilentCJ is a god and did it perfect[br][br][size=1]Posted on: April 23, 2009, 05:47:19 pm[/size][hr]Wow i truly thought more people would want elite XD meh i am working on Corrupted at the moment i have completed the drop set (this time with correct drop and female models) And i just have the weapons to go. When they are done i am gonna do the bodies and legs of the PvP armors
